      • createCandle

        public Candle createCandle(java.lang.String color,
                           int size,
                           java.lang.String essence,
                           double illuminanceDegree)
        This method creates and then returns a candle.
        Post:A candle is created.
        Parameters:
        color. - String with the color of the candle.
        size. - A number representing the size of the candle. Must be between 1 and 3.
        essence. - A String with the essence of the candle.
        illuminanceDegree. - A Rational number representing the illuminance degree of the candle. In lux.
        Returns:
        A candle object.
